data.description: If you're looking for 6+ secluded acres with trees, a seasonal creek, room for horses, cows, chickens and more this doublewide mobile home is just what you're looking for.  Or you can live in it while you build your dream home amongst the trees and wildlife.  The roof was replaced on the doublewide  in 2019, new skirting, recently leveled, new floors in all but 3 rooms in 2022.  Shed and carport have electricity plus there is a chicken coop and several small lean-to's for storage. Interested in the tiny home...ask Agent for more information.  Located in the highly sought after Poolville ISD, with no HOA and no restrictions this beautiful property has the potential and privacy to be whatever you've been dreaming of.
